Description: 

Which of the boys while at a young age, has not dreamed to wear uniforms equipment lifeguard boat hook arm and fire hydrant, at breakneck speed to climb the ladder sliding towards the dangers for the salvation of others? In the next sequel of the popular series, studio Sixteen Tons Entertainment present new Emergency 5 for the PC, allowing the player to enjoy all the marvels of this work lifeguard and experience first hand what heroism - is not an empty word, and the hard work that is given only a strong spirit people . At this time, rescue operations will be held in the three metropolitan areas of Germany - Berlin, Hamburg and Munich. Under the guidance of Emergency Player 5 will be a fleet of rescue equipment to be properly dispose of and resolve the situation. The game is endowed with the possibility of cooperative transmission, which will join forces with four of his friends or colleagues Features: - 4 cities for your home Shoigu (Berlin, Hamburg, Munich and Cologne - the last available just in Deluxe-version of the game)



- 10 different accidents and 50 incidents will not get bored
- Full control over the fire, skorymy, rescue teams and police
